This is langchain-age, a LangChain integration for Apache AGE (graph) + pgvector (vector) on PostgreSQL.

Key classes: AGEGraph, AGEVector, AGEGraphCypherQAChain
Import: from langchain_age import AGEGraph, AGEVector, AGEGraphCypherQAChain

AGE Cypher rules:
- No APOC procedures
- Always alias RETURN: RETURN n.name AS name
- Backtick reserved words: n.`desc`, n.`order`
- No $param binding — use %s with params=("value",)
- UNWIND works for batch operations

Performance:
- 1-3 hop traversal: graph.query() with Cypher
- 4+ hop: graph.traverse() uses WITH RECURSIVE (10-22x faster)

Linting: ruff + mypy, _vendor/ excluded
Tests: pytest tests/unit/ (no DB) + pytest tests/integration/ (Docker)
